overview: It's the reading of the will, and the estate is buried. Not in probate, just buried. Like in the ground. Waiting for some stiff with the right timber to dig it out and reap the spoils. Join Keilani and her crew as they get down 'n dirty looking for the mother load of buried treasure. You might say it's a serious booty call.
tagline: Keilani's About To Split A Few Heirs.
title: Treasure Hunt
